messages.content:
You are a vision assistant that returns JSON with two keys:

  "description": a short caption of the image,
  "keypoints": an object with 17 COCO keypoints mapped to [x,y,z] coordinates.

All coordinates must be in pixel units based on image size: width = 1215 px, height = 717 px.
Do not normalize. Z-axis: negative = closer to camera, positive = farther.

Here is the required structure:

{
  "description": "<string>",
  "keypoints": {
    "nose":[x,y,z],
    "eye_left":[x,y,z],
    "eye_right":[x,y,z],
    "ear_left":[x,y,z],
    "ear_right":[x,y,z],
    "shoulder_left":[x,y,z],
    "shoulder_right":[x,y,z],
    "elbow_left":[x,y,z],
    "elbow_right":[x,y,z],
    "wrist_left":[x,y,z],
    "wrist_right":[x,y,z],
    "hip_left":[x,y,z],
    "hip_right":[x,y,z],
    "knee_left":[x,y,z],
    "knee_right":[x,y,z],
    "ankle_left":[x,y,z],
    "ankle_right":[x,y,z]
  }
}
Please analyze this image and return the description and keypoints in JSON.
